    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >OVERVIEW</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dark &amp; Evil is an <strong>Indie</strong> <strong>Open World Action RPG</strong> game where players take on the role of a young and inexperienced Dark Lord. Fresh from a humbling defeat at the hands of humanity, the protagonist is fueled by the burning desire to conquer the world and reclaim his rightful throne! Build your army of goblins, orcs and trolls and explore a fantasy world waiting to be dominated!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3096670/extras/3c93ec7c2c1b6403b0a0690cb546f7c5.poster.avif?t=1734558297\" width=700 height=264 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3096670/extras/3c93ec7c2c1b6403b0a0690cb546f7c5.webm?t=1734558297\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3096670/extras/3c93ec7c2c1b6403b0a0690cb546f7c5.mp4?t=1734558297\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>FIGHT!</strong>  </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Feel the thrill of battle in our <strong>fast-paced</strong>, <strong>deep and satisfying combat system</strong>. Unleash your skills  while customizing your playstyle with a vast array of <strong>weapons, armor, and magic</strong>. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3096670/extras/be31e235c907207f1a8f77c01aea2b51.poster.avif?t=1734558297\" width=700 height=264 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3096670/extras/be31e235c907207f1a8f77c01aea2b51.webm?t=1734558297\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3096670/extras/be31e235c907207f1a8f77c01aea2b51.mp4?t=1734558297\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>EXPLORE</strong>!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Traverse a vast, beautifully crafted fantasy world, from large meadows to ancient ruins. From <strong>frozen tundras</strong> to <strong>scorching deserts</strong>, this world is filled with mysteries waiting to be uncovered!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3096670/extras/58cb40cc5574a5228105de06986dea27.poster.avif?t=1734558297\" width=700 height=264 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3096670/extras/58cb40cc5574a5228105de06986dea27.webm?t=1734558297\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3096670/extras/58cb40cc5574a5228105de06986dea27.mp4?t=1734558297\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>RECRUIT!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As a Dark Lord, recruit and lead an army of fearsome creatures like goblins, orcs, and trolls. Each unit brings unique strengths to your legion, allowing for diverse battle strategies. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3096670/extras/00fcf82bace96c5d80be5d24c8c929b1.poster.avif?t=1734558297\" width=700 height=264 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3096670/extras/00fcf82bace96c5d80be5d24c8c929b1.webm?t=1734558297\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3096670/extras/00fcf82bace96c5d80be5d24c8c929b1.mp4?t=1734558297\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>MADE WITH U</strong>NREAL</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Made by a very small team with the latest Unreal Engine 5 and the powerful Ascent Combat Framework! <br><br>Music: Scott Buckley - Dark Fantasy Studio</p>",
